<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-08-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-08-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="761" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d761">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">701.0090/1794: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Harrison</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-24">August 24,
                                        1943</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>2056. American interests Philippines repatriation. Your 5135, August
                                    21.<note n="93" xml:id="d761fn93">Not printed; it reported
                                    Japanese deletion of names of 13 Philippine citizens trom the
                                    list of persons to be repatriated from occupied China.</note>
                                The Philippine citizens in question are nationals of the United
                                States and accordingly entitled under the exchange agreement to be
                                exchanged. It is requested that the Swiss Legation Tokyo so inform
                                the Japanese Government.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Berle</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>